imdb.plot outline: An animated series that follows four great friends navigating not only the twists and turns of the course, but the comically poignant challenges of life as men. The male-bonding on the golf course acts as a priceless oasis amidst the chaotic mire of marriages, relationships, work and kids. It is the beating heart of their manhood (and sometimes their manhood needs a little beating.)
